      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways! It runs smooth, looks great, and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
