    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and balanced weight distribution this chassis is famous for. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the critical VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, and the cooling system has been refreshed to handle spirited driving. A mechanically honest platform for the purist looking for an engaging, analog experience.",
